text.text: I ORDERED THE TRAP SUPER POSE, I WAITED FOR 60 DAYS AND I BOUGHT IT, THE RIFLE ARRIVED DEFECTIVE AFTER I RECEIVED IT, THE BOTTOM NEEDLE IS NOT FIRING AND THE RIFLE DOES NOT CLOSE. I WANTED A WIDE BAND, SO WE IGNORED IT, I SENT IT AGAIN, AND AGAIN IT LEFT ME HALF-WAY IN A TRAP COMPETITION. I SENT IT AGAIN, THE RESULT IS Frustrated AGAIN, I CAME Frustrated FROM EVERY TRAP COMPETITION TO BERATTA AND RIZZINIYE I DECIDED NOT TO STAY CALM BECAUSE IT'S CHEAP. IF YOU NEED TO PAY 20 THOUSAND AND 25 THOUSAND DO NOT BUY THIS BRAND BEFORE THIS I HAD A POSITION CALLED AKSA CROSFIRE AND HE DID NOT MAKE THE SMALLEST MISTAKE.
